  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/cb58b0f43f63ca4ac7391c9d836a5b19.poster.avif?t=1695326058\" width=616 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/cb58b0f43f63ca4ac7391c9d836a5b19.webm?t=1695326058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/cb58b0f43f63ca4ac7391c9d836a5b19.mp4?t=1695326058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hanger World is an awesome ragdoll swinging action game with crazy physics!<br><br>• <strong>SWING</strong> your ragdoll through dangerous levels filled with razor sharp spikes, buzz saws, lethal lasers, hungry monsters and all sorts of limb cutting obstacles!<br><br>• <strong>CREATE</strong> your own levels and share them with your friends!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br>• <strong>100+</strong> Hanger killing levels!<br>• <strong>Level Editor!</strong> Create and share your levels with others!<br>• <strong>Speedrun Mode</strong> on all levels - Get the best time!<br>• Unlock <strong>cool rewards</strong> for your Hanger!<br>• Powered by state of the art <strong>Ragdoll Limb Cutting Technology™!</strong><br>• Swing around like a <strong>Stickman Ragdoll Spider Man!</strong><br>• Music by <strong>Boy vs Bacteria!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/391ca4022937f65e7eebeb874d6b8ecd.poster.avif?t=1695326058\" width=618 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/391ca4022937f65e7eebeb874d6b8ecd.webm?t=1695326058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/391ca4022937f65e7eebeb874d6b8ecd.mp4?t=1695326058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE HISTORY OF HANGER</h2><br>From hugely successful flash games with millions of plays to featured mobile games with millions of downloads and now back to desktop again - The Hanger games has had great success on every platform that they've been released on so far and now Hanger World is finally coming to Steam!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/4e4d6fa80d6797e958cd4606f60d913e.avif?t=1695326058\" width=590 height=166 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/5b5226c0a8ed96a2b92e21169893643b.webp?t=1695326058\" width=590 height=50 /></span><br><br><strong>Keep on Swingin'!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/cb58b0f43f63ca4ac7391c9d836a5b19.poster.avif?t=1695326058\" width=616 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/cb58b0f43f63ca4ac7391c9d836a5b19.webm?t=1695326058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/cb58b0f43f63ca4ac7391c9d836a5b19.mp4?t=1695326058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hanger World is an awesome ragdoll swinging action game with crazy physics!<br><br>• <strong>SWING</strong> your ragdoll through dangerous levels filled with razor sharp spikes, buzz saws, lethal lasers, hungry monsters and all sorts of limb cutting obstacles!<br><br>• <strong>CREATE</strong> your own levels and share them with your friends!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br>• <strong>100+</strong> Hanger killing levels!<br>• <strong>Level Editor!</strong> Create and share your levels with others!<br>• <strong>Speedrun Mode</strong> on all levels - Get the best time!<br>• Unlock <strong>cool rewards</strong> for your Hanger!<br>• Powered by state of the art <strong>Ragdoll Limb Cutting Technology™!</strong><br>• Swing around like a <strong>Stickman Ragdoll Spider Man!</strong><br>• Music by <strong>Boy vs Bacteria!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/391ca4022937f65e7eebeb874d6b8ecd.poster.avif?t=1695326058\" width=618 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/391ca4022937f65e7eebeb874d6b8ecd.webm?t=1695326058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/391ca4022937f65e7eebeb874d6b8ecd.mp4?t=1695326058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE HISTORY OF HANGER</h2><br>From hugely successful flash games with millions of plays to featured mobile games with millions of downloads and now back to desktop again - The Hanger games has had great success on every platform that they've been released on so far and now Hanger World is finally coming to Steam!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/4e4d6fa80d6797e958cd4606f60d913e.avif?t=1695326058\" width=590 height=166 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/484390/extras/5b5226c0a8ed96a2b92e21169893643b.webp?t=1695326058\" width=590 height=50 /></span><br><br><strong>Keep on Swingin'!</strong>",
